{"id":"fd10a146e9625bfd3f69639eeb5fbee0eae7e4633222f1ee3d3d36395844303e","item_id":"dccfa09313:0","text":"Materials（材质）"}
{"id":"c526885593bfd2479e93b156b6cbfd499d79ac815ae1ecd4a244912247a13f6e","item_id":"dccfa09313:1","text":"Materials（材质）在 RenderMan 中通常称为 Bxdf(s)。Bxdf 会向"}
{"id":"168196d133817ed25c3fe0bf9a5254309ab899daa622e81d3ead0daf0eb33def","item_id":"dccfa09313:2","text":"integrator（积分器）"}
{"id":"02152c3eabbe86a204b0ed0bba009c1e795fff0f5fccd55c053b1b1d8b881ade","item_id":"dccfa09313:3","text":"描述材质，并由该积分器决定最终渲染外观。由于二者彼此独立，用户可以更换积分器，同时仍使用同一个 Bxdf 来获得一致或预期的结果。假设你创建了一种金色金属；如果用 PxrPathTracer 或 PxrVCM 渲染它，你会期望最终图像中的材质属性仍然呈现为 \"gold\"（金色）。这甚至可以扩展到非照片写实积分器和 custom（自定义）积分器：它们可以用新的、有趣的方式渲染你的 gold Bxdf（金色 Bxdf），但结果仍会被理解为 gold（黄金/金色）。这正是 RenderMan 中材质 Bxdfs 的能力。"}
{"id":"ac28c531421f2d044d172e7fd699dceb991d423da9731101a5c331de95f51b7b","item_id":"dccfa09313:4","text":"下面的链接按常见用途分类列出 RenderMan 中可用的材质。"}
{"id":"8608905e6533fb79c29dcbee9e54642763cc7988fd456046ba16656c6564e8fd","item_id":"dccfa09313:5","text":"PxrSurface"}
{"id":"ebe46811da2358beaedf1a7442f06c90316cc30c85460c1d18a970711da706eb","item_id":"dccfa09313:6","text":"- 这是用于创建所需各种外观的终极材质系统。从皮肤到宝石，PxrSurface 都能通过分层和艺术家驱动参数处理复杂外观。"}
{"id":"7c18b2214d97ef7458b3ebb76731e758dfc77c1c5b2f254e019754aa848d2b67","item_id":"dccfa09313:7","text":"MaterialX Lama"}
{"id":"da6fb6837d64707bff06d6fcf318a0c0d1782cfaff9936d73aac5d320163bbea","item_id":"dccfa09313:8","text":"MaterialX Lama 是 Industrial Light & Magic 开发的先进材质分层系统；它引入了一种模块化方式来构建材质网络，并包含关于能量守恒和色散的近期工作。"}
{"id":"6b2b3cbd4ad476016050e61b781d1112117b06945fb578fbffcfc4ff3f6daa69","item_id":"dccfa09313:9","text":"PxrVolume"}
{"id":"03380220a988aa802f37a7f21ac64be8b5496728f1dbb239e265effbcfe6b6a6","item_id":"dccfa09313:10","text":"- 一种强大且快速的体积着色器，用于烟、火、爆炸等效果。"}
{"id":"ccf31fc48275c143b867da4b33a4ee3f6d4e505c6b15e85616384686e98b23fe","item_id":"dccfa09313:11","text":"PxrMarschnerHair"}
{"id":"f362e0e87c7b09d58543a200a9c9c4ddf6432f87593b54e5dacdd29c1a3d7618","item_id":"dccfa09313:12","text":"- 此材质专为毛发、绒毛和纤维设计。"}
{"id":"f380d30f8481b984621452835584792ce119bc8c4fd19bc2bff61812052f6f83","item_id":"dccfa09313:13","text":"Basic Materials（基础材质）"}
{"id":"b2796e3f880ca72d3907b2b74e45a81e18509f6eb7d8f8971cbc1a3b959439f9","item_id":"dccfa09313:14","text":"- 这些材质面向特定用途设计。"}
{"id":"20f53349b9fef849eb5e27f738ed21d56ab95a3635ae66bd3c0a614058279948","item_id":"dccfa09313:15","text":"PxrConstant"}
{"id":"bffd31a1071728d658cf0fb6890da0401a71478ac2c45233936ee2b0ec4d0240","item_id":"dccfa09313:16","text":"- 此材质提供恒定颜色，也可以贴图化。它非常适合投影以及其他不希望出现着色的效果。"}
{"id":"989730b0317d6d4e5c702f6ba2ef05b9b93f02c3c3ef1eba4d57eb929ea2df03","item_id":"dccfa09313:17","text":"PxrDiffuse"}
{"id":"171524ae3b553c9aa657ee9fa299fef495f002da3f740976f50b8fae3d102420","item_id":"dccfa09313:18","text":"- 一种简单且快速的漫反射材质。"}
{"id":"ca6e9359019eea08d170f12ef85506fb6ede83064a7deed0382b113f737f6a97","item_id":"dccfa09313:19","text":"PxrBlack"}
{"id":"250eb2c542517f9b9ad24ee1236cb1847b7a93ce4d59f54102a40011c8194eb0","item_id":"dccfa09313:20","text":"- 一种非散射材质，顾名思义会渲染为黑色。"}
{"id":"ec83c6ad191cfd06bd60e2de67611d7d253276d23b688761fe69baa7e3a4f5f6","item_id":"dccfa09313:21","text":"Texture Manager（纹理管理器）"}
{"id":"6a6418ba097cbea8e3a21d1d4886992c020645f9f906159bfa4f9089e775e990","item_id":"dccfa09313:22","text":"Volume Material（体积材质）"}
{"id":"5562801c46d604d1f5f40f1b53a83bf1c84dcf61251b187a5617341903e32bee","item_id":"dccfa09313:23","text":"Soloing Patterns（单独显示 Patterns）"}
{"id":"16eadb67c73036050c32d8ae0da4ddb676c856f047ee2bfa318e741f0c89beb5","item_id":"dccfa09313:24","text":"OSL Patterns（OSL Patterns 图案）"}
{"id":"266b1ff1611fec62ab74724391470f582b02a1e9bbaa4b0c304f58873fc4cf18","item_id":"dccfa09313:25","text":"Assigning Materials To Faces（将材质指定到面）"}
{"id":"272660cb28d95651dd54848e5e4ee359a4c63ad01773d96b8dd26612ed880b2b","item_id":"dccfa09313:26","text":"Using Material Layers（使用材质层）"}
{"id":"b87a1e22bd9021e12a42194207cbad5bf84677c4448ff88b8f8343d6310e9e56","item_id":"dccfa09313:27","text":"Using Displacement（使用置换）"}
{"id":"02775c2d16f1aa0b2f7b7ba56ac4785260062bfce052dc25592d8bc85fd8a7e1","item_id":"dccfa09313:28","text":"Creating A Material（创建材质）"}
